snippet: Irish Whiskey Cask Scottish Stout and Concannon Irish Whiskey arrive in stores.
abstract: Irish Whiskey Cask Scottish Stout, made by Innis & Gunn, and Concannon Irish Whiskey, made at the Cooley Distillery in County Louth, Ireland, bring Irish cheer to America for St Patrick's Day.
lead_paragraph: Irish Whiskey Cask Scottish Stout and Concannon Irish Whiskey arrive in stores.
